metadata.name: Gramps in Paradise
metadata.description: Robbie "Gramps" Mattson is here in Web3 to make a difference.  I choose to LeadwithLove everyday.  I chose to always do the next right thing, always.  I believe in the Future and know that we can make it together.  I am planning to use my ASSets to grow the communities I am a part of.  There will come a time when you will be able to "burn" this token for another token if you chose to.  No one was meant to be offended by this picture.
